latestPosts.caption:
And the award goes to `Pooja Budhraja ‘ !! ✨

I am beyond thrilled to share that I’ve been awarded Emerging Makeup Artist of the Year – West! ✨✨ Still processing that this is real!

Three years ago, when I first began this journey, I knew I had something special in me, but never imagined I’d be here today. It’s been a rollercoaster of emotions leading up to this moment, and I can’t thank all of you enough for your endless support. ♥️

A huge shoutout to my Dad, my constant pillar of strength – this one’s for you. ♥️

This is truly just the beginning, and I’m so excited for what lies ahead! 🤞🤞

A big thank you to @cosmoindia for recognizing my work. Here’s to many more moments like this! ✨☺️

Outfit @mannat_boutique_ 
Jewellery @just_lil_things_ 
Bag @forever21_in

20K STRONG🧿♥️

**“I could’ve thrown a party, dressed up, called people, made it grand… but honestly, this is what felt right.
A simple cake. Ghar ke kapde. My family around me., the ones who never gave up on me ♥️
This 20K didn’t happen overnight. It took me 3 years — of showing up, breaking down, starting again.

This cake is for every late night edit, every video that didn’t perform, every time I kept going anyway.
Thank you, 20,000 of you — for making space for me, just as I am.♥️

Cheers to the girl who kept showing up even when no one was watching 🧿
From here - there’s only going up ⭐️✨

#universehasyourback #trustyourpath #joyinthejourney #thankyoueveryone #thanksforyoursupport
